  $
    accent(a, arrow)_1 = vec(1, 3) quad quad "and" quad quad accent(a, arrow)_2 = vec(2, 6)
  $

  The column space, denoted $"Col"(A)$, is the span of these two vectors:

  $
    "Col"(A) = "span"({vec(1, 3), vec(2, 6)})
