$m times n$ matrix:

$
A = mat(
  a_(1 1), a_(1 2), ..., a_(1 m);
  a_(2 1), a_(2 2), ..., a_(2 m);
  dots.v, dots.v, dots.down, dots.v;
  a_(n 1), a_(n 2), dots.h, a_(n m);
)
