$n times p$ matrix:

$
B = mat(
  a_(1 1), a_(1 2), ..., a_(1 p);
  a_(2 1), a_(2 2), ..., a_(2 p);
  dots.v, dots.v, dots.down, dots.v;
  a_(n 1), a_(n 2), dots.h, a_(n p);
)
$

Compute Each Element of Result Matrix $C$

$
c_(i j) = sum_(k=1)^n = a_(i k) b_(k j)
$

